{
  "name": "Sanguine Swords",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "type": "String",
      "label": "Description",
      "value": "<p>You summon a magical red sword that hovers in front of you. Each additional +2 SL on your Casting Test allows you to summon an extra sword (maximum 6 swords).</p><p>On every subsequent round, you can spend your action to direct the swords against targets within range and line of sight. A target can only be attacked by one sword at a time. The swords possess the @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.items.EO05HX7jql0g605A]{Fly (20)} Creature Trait and strike with Weapon Skill 60 and deal 8 Damage before returning quickly to you. Sanguine Swords can be defended against normally and do not accrue Advantage. The swords can be dispelled but are otherwise indestructible.</p><p><strong>Lore:</strong> You may inflict +1 @Condition[Ablaze] Condition on anyone targeted by spells from the Lore of Fire, unless they also possess the Arcane Magic (Fire) Talent. Every Ablaze condition within Willpower Bonus yards adds +10 to attempts to Channel or Cast with Aqshy.</p><p></p>"
    },
